    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "For sale is a well-maintained vehicle in good overall condition. This car has been cared for and remains reliable for daily use. The exterior is in great shape, though you might find a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is solid; it has a complete service history and has recently undergone a routine inspection. It drives smoothly and needs nothing to be enjoyed immediately. This is a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable, high-quality vehicle without the premium price of a showroom-new model.",
      "price": 34500.0,
