      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior paint still holds a nice shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches from normal car washes. There are no major dents or structural issues. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather seats show some light creasing on the driver's side bolster but remain soft and comfortable. All power features, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully functional. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly with a consistent service history, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that presents very well for its age.",
      "price": 3450.0,
