      "description": "Oh man, you have to see this car! It is seriously in pristine, mint condition\u2014honestly, it\u2019s like brand new. I\u2019ve babied this thing since day one, and it shows. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s flawless and ready for the road, this is the one. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
