    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of precision engineering, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with its individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS system in peak operational state. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by a meticulously maintained suspension, while the Getrag six-speed manual gearbox offers tactile, short-throw engagement. Every mechanical element, from the reinforced rear subframe to the variable M differential lock, has been preserved to factory tolerances. This vehicle boasts an unblemished service history, documented thermal cycles, and a pristine undercarriage, representing a true turnkey investment for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
